---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../config/site-config";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description={`About ${siteConfig.siteName}: who we are and how we pick products.`}
>
  <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-900">About</h1>
  <div class="prose prose-emerald">
    <p>
      {siteConfig.siteName} publishes equipment decision guides for planted
      freshwater aquariums. The approach is opinionated and narrow: we focus
      on gear that matters for planted tanks, and we compare products against
      specific tank setups (size, planting density, livestock) rather than
      ranking them in the abstract.
    </p>
    <h2>How we pick</h2>
    <p>
      Picks draw on published specifications, hobbyist community consensus from
      forums like r/PlantedTank and the Barr Report, long-run reputation across
      brands, and product fit against the specific use case described on each
      page. We do not receive products for review and we are not sponsored.
    </p>
    <p>
      We participate in the Amazon Associates program. When you buy through
      links on this site, we earn a small commission at no cost to you. That
      doesn't change our picks. It pays for the time to keep them up to date.
    </p>
    <h2>Limitations</h2>
    <p>
      We don't hands-on test every product. Specifications are drawn from
      manufacturer sources, which occasionally overstate performance (flow
      rates, especially). Use our picks as a starting point, read the product's
      own documentation, and measure parameters in your own tank.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email corrections to <em>corrections@{siteConfig.domain}</em>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
